19// Copies characters from a CFStringRef into a std::string.
20std::string CFStringToString(const CFStringRef cf_string) {
21 RTC_DCHECK(cf_string);
22 std::string std_string;
23 // Get the size needed for UTF8 plus terminating character.
24 size_t buffer_size =
25 CFStringGetMaximumSizeForEncoding(CFStringGetLength(cf_string),
26 kCFStringEncodingUTF8) +
27 1;
28 std::unique_ptr<char[]> buffer(new char[buffer_size]);
29 if (CFStringGetCString(cf_string, buffer.get(), buffer_size,
30 kCFStringEncodingUTF8)) {
31 // Copy over the characters.
32 std_string.assign(buffer.get());
33 }
34 return std_string;
35}

37// Convenience function for setting a VT property.
38void SetVTSessionProperty(VTCompressionSessionRef vtSession, VCPCompressionSessionRef vcpSession,
39 CFStringRef key,
40 int32_t value) {
41 RTC_DCHECK(vtSession || vcpSession);
42 CFNumberRef cfNum =
43 CFNumberCreate(kCFAllocatorDefault, kCFNumberSInt32Type, &value);
44 OSStatus status = noErr;
45 if (vtSession)
46 status = VTSessionSetProperty(vtSession, key, cfNum);
47#if ENABLE_VCP_ENCODER
48 else
49 status = webrtc::VCPCompressionSessionSetProperty(vcpSession, key, cfNum);
50#endif
51 CFRelease(cfNum);
52 if (status != noErr) {
53 std::string key_string = CFStringToString(key);
54 RTC_LOG(LS_ERROR) << "VTSessionSetProperty failed to set: " << key_string
55 << " to " << value << ": " << status;
56 }
57}
58
59// Convenience function for setting a VT property.
60void SetVTSessionProperty(VTCompressionSessionRef vtSession, VCPCompressionSessionRef vcpSession,
61 CFStringRef key,
62 uint32_t value) {
63 RTC_DCHECK(vtSession || vcpSession);
64 int64_t value_64 = value;
65 CFNumberRef cfNum =
66 CFNumberCreate(kCFAllocatorDefault, kCFNumberSInt64Type, &value_64);
67 OSStatus status = noErr;
68 if (vtSession)
69 status = VTSessionSetProperty(vtSession, key, cfNum);
70#if ENABLE_VCP_ENCODER
71 else
72 status = webrtc::VCPCompressionSessionSetProperty(vcpSession, key, cfNum);
73#endif
74 CFRelease(cfNum);
75 if (status != noErr) {
76 std::string key_string = CFStringToString(key);
77 RTC_LOG(LS_ERROR) << "VTSessionSetProperty failed to set: " << key_string
78 << " to " << value << ": " << status;
79 }
80}

82// Convenience function for setting a VT property.
83void SetVTSessionProperty(VTCompressionSessionRef vtSession, VCPCompressionSessionRef vcpSession, CFStringRef key, bool value) {
84 RTC_DCHECK(vtSession || vcpSession);
85 CFBooleanRef cf_bool = (value) ? kCFBooleanTrue : kCFBooleanFalse;
86 OSStatus status = noErr;
87 if (vtSession)
88 status = VTSessionSetProperty(vtSession, key, cf_bool);
89#if ENABLE_VCP_ENCODER
90 else
91 status = webrtc::VCPCompressionSessionSetProperty(vcpSession, key, cf_bool);
92#endif
93 if (status != noErr) {
94 std::string key_string = CFStringToString(key);
95 RTC_LOG(LS_ERROR) << "VTSessionSetProperty failed to set: " << key_string
96 << " to " << value << ": " << status;
97 }
98}

100// Convenience function for setting a VT property.
101void SetVTSessionProperty(VTCompressionSessionRef vtSession, VCPCompressionSessionRef vcpSession,
102 CFStringRef key,
103 CFStringRef value) {
104 RTC_DCHECK(vtSession || vcpSession);
105 OSStatus status = noErr;
106 if (vtSession)
107 status = VTSessionSetProperty(vtSession, key, value);
108#if ENABLE_VCP_ENCODER
109 else
110 status = webrtc::VCPCompressionSessionSetProperty(vcpSession, key, value);
111#endif
112 if (status != noErr) {
113 std::string key_string = CFStringToString(key);
114 std::string val_string = CFStringToString(value);
115 RTC_LOG(LS_ERROR) << "VTSessionSetProperty failed to set: " << key_string
116 << " to " << val_string << ": " << status;
117 }
118}

120// Convenience function for setting a VT property.
121void SetVTSessionProperty(VTCompressionSessionRef vtSession, VCPCompressionSessionRef vcpSession,
122 CFStringRef key,
123 CFArrayRef value) {
124 RTC_DCHECK(vtSession || vcpSession);
125 OSStatus status = noErr;
126 if (vtSession)
127 status = VTSessionSetProperty(vtSession, key, value);
128#if ENABLE_VCP_ENCODER
129 else
130 status = webrtc::VCPCompressionSessionSetProperty(vcpSession, key, value);
131#endif
132
133 if (status != noErr) {
134 std::string key_string = CFStringToString(key);
135 RTC_LOG(LS_ERROR) << "VTSessionSetProperty failed to set: " << key_string
136 << " to array value: " << status << ", vcpSession: " << vcpSession;
137 }
